{"tid":649563,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[遲咗sor]17-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強次回合--周子瑜@TWICE 對 新垣結衣","createTime":"2018-05-01T16:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T14:31:45.000Z","uid":92376,"like":91,"dislike":125,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c543766fbb1b1685373ed7131ce3848f850f65a6","tid":649563,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T16:20:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n周子瑜@TWICE v 新垣結衣<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強次回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-5-2 12:20am-10:20pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DYoMUFh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDYoMUFh.png&h=8e122659&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HIUU4il.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHIUU4il.png&h=1decc683&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/c4H073L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc4H073L.png&h=24615d99&s={SIZE}\" />周子瑜@TWICE v 新垣結衣<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fDKJUOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfDKJUOh.png&h=cf9c1fd7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(首回合 189-214)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"6e6c